Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relying on numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:13.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These are The Dollars?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:15.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't all be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:18.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, you could marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:21.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you keeping our secret about "that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:22.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:25.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is much more fun than I thought it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:28.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm screaming that, "I've been born right here and now!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Celty back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:07.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:13.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for you, my sister would've locked \Nher away in that cramped research facility again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:14.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, give Celty back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to run away with her somewhere before the police arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:25.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:31.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've watched her since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:33.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to set her free...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To let her run free in a wide-open world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:38.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd live there with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:43.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always, always, always, always, always, \Nalways been thinking nothing but those thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:48.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop the power of love, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In contrast to that, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:54.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You relied only on strength in numbers both then and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My love won't fall apart so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel pain, but I'll forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for pain in the life I'll lead with Celty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:11.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I won't feel the pain you're dishing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:12.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:27.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:32.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji is strict, violent, and different from \Nmost people, but he's not a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:36.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he has someone he likes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.65,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be! It couldn't be! It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:38.25,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not her. That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.74,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...not my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.56,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.97,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima...Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:59.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Harima Mika, the girl who Seiji supposedly killed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:04.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:06.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:08.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:11.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're there, aren't you, Seiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, you forgot to leave the door unlocked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't come in if you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:25.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji, I sat next to you during our entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:30.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the person on my right had\N the awesome name "Ryugamine Mikado..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:33.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered what kind of name the person to my left had...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I glanced over, I fell in love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You even smiled when our eyes met, Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please show yourself, Seiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you're not opening the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:50.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll open it for you. Just wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:52.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:58.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked into some things after that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:01.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like your birthday, and stuff about your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Se-Seiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, err, I, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:21.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, I won't tell anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:23.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, umm, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:26.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll grow to like what you like,\N no matter what hobbies you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:29.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:32.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:43.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, your sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want Seiji to like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And...and there was a doctor there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:06:01.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said with a little cosmetic surgery and some makeup, I'd look just like that head—the head you're in love with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:05.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "You're Celty now, since that's what its name is."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:09.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I tried to be like Celty for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Namie said that wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:16.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said you'd figure that out, so they'd use surgery\N and medication to make my memory disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:23.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't want to lose my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.65,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who knows my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:23.19,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A doctor who knows I'm a dullahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:27.94,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one person like that in this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:29.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I went through all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:45.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you couldn't distinguish the impostor from the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean that's all your love amounted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:59.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I think it's amazing that you\N risked your life trying to get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I misunderstood you, Harima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:07.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've certainly got some personality \Nproblems, but you're definitely not a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:14.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you put your life on the line for him, which \Nis something you probably can't do out of selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:18.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you still love the guy who almost killed you is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In many different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:25.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima, I think you're a lot like Yagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:31.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to say, "What's the meaning of this," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And next, you'd say:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:46.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"So, you knew that my head was in that research facility."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:50.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"So, both you and your father were colluding with Yagiri Pharmaceuticals."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:54.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your father was probably the one who stole my head!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:08:00.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yet you hid that from me and cut up a dying girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:05.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I may be a monster, but chewing up and \Nspitting out humans makes you the real monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:10.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I'll say this in advance to clear up any misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:14.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I neither know nor care whether my\N father was the one who stole your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:18.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the girl wanted us to perform that minor surgery on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:21.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Yagiri people may have guided her towards that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:30.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Can you understand what I'm thinking?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved you for twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'd understand something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you keep quiet about the location of my head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:47.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I kept quiet about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd go off somewhere if you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:56.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say I'll give up so you can be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:09:00.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our love for each other is at stake in this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:03.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:11.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To make sure I don't, I'll exploit others' love, their deaths,\N myself, and—this may sound contradictory—but even your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:19.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I get my head back, I wouldn't ever think of leaving—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:23.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if that's what you think, your head might not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:31.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did a faerie like you appear in front of humans in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:37.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you were able to manifest yourself in this world precisely because you've lost your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:44.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe once your head is back in your hands and your \Nmemory returns, you'll fade from this world like a puff of smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...as if everything that happened up until now was an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:00.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you believe what I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:05.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conversely, you're the only person I don't distrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:15.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that there's no one here who can kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not boasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:20.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept it as a simple fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:23.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no joy or feeling in my acceptance of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:27.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But—or maybe because of that—I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:31.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no core inside of me that controls my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:34.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My head itself is that nucleus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone were to destroy that core...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:41.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, regardless of my will or situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:49.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nightmares even though I don't have eyes or a brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:53.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you believe in someone who\N trembles in fear at the nightmares she sees?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:59.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been afraid of that, so I've been \Nsearching for my head in order to control my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:02.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I said that, would you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:07.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it, didn't I? You're the only one I believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:09.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a complete loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:13.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so stubborn that we never leave the realm of speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shinra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me punch you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:25.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:32.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, now let me punch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:47.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you're most beautiful when you're honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:53.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That punch was a substitute for our wedding kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:21.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that's pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:29.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dotachin. Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:34.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you know how The Dollars got its name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:36.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it from, "Give me your dollars!" or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:41.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the organization basically doesn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're "The Dollars" because they lounge around going "dara dara."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dotachin, did you see that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The black biker—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, was that real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't just some illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was some CG kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:58.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That CG thing is in The Dollars, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:03.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.17,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:09.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honestly surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:13.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew lots of people online claim to be in The Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:19.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I didn't realize so many people\N would come to an impromptu gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans truly exceed my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:31.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you have some dream about escaping everyday life,\N but life in Tokyo will become routine for you after six months or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:39.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, if you want to reach the non-everyday, you'll either have to move somewhere else or get into more "underground" things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:44.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But once you step into that world, it'll only take about three days for that to seem normal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:51.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly want to continue escaping from everyday life, you've no other choice but to keep evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:54.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter whether you're aiming higher or lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy everyday life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:09.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of respect for you, I gave you Yagiri Namie's phone number \Nfor free, and I won't tell anyone you're the founder of The Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:13.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it when you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,IIIzaaayaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:25.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's apparently time for our meeting to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:29.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Tanaka Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,IIIzaaayaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:41.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:47.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, life returned to being astonishingly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.51,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,For him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.06,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.13,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as the boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:56.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw on the Net that The Dollars had a get-together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:15:01.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And apparently, Simon and Shizuo are in The Dollars as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I heard that the black biker has no head,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:04.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she drove down a wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:05.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,pulled out a huge scythe,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:08.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone was like, "Bwaah,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and it was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get any of what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And for them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:16.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:22.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't forget my love for her when I'm looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:25.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll accept your love for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:28.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I can get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.22,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(275,230)}Tanaka Taro has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:39.49,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:41.36,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Evenin'. I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.49,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:45.20,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty tired today, so I'll be signing off early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.91,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you didn't get much sleep?\N Did you pull an all-nighter or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:49.34,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.51,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Kanra isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.54,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanra...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.00,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,...will come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:56.71,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, something just came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:58.01,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.14,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I've got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.48,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:02.77,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(275,230)}Setton has left the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to intrude on your fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an urgent job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:09.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:13.95,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, my everyday life is continuing on like it always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:18.33,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I bump into people I\N don't want to meet hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the whole thing's been dispelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:28.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ghosts are scary because they always sneak around, \Nthen appear out of nowhere, and you made quite the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:32.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will be afraid of you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:34.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, you didn't kill anyone, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that scythe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:36.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it even cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you chasing that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can help out whenever you need me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:42.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:46.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:49.77,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where Yagiri Namie is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.43,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:54.28,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I am who I am, and there's nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.56,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The days continue like they always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:59.16,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They bring neither excessive desire nor despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.70,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:05.29,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I'm overwhelmed with a sense of fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:07.17,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.92,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,You're over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:13.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm your savior, then you're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.58,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the boy contemplated things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:22.06,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He thought about what Orihara Izaya said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:28.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Could the boy who yearned for an unbelievable \Nreality continue to seek new ones for all eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:33.17,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And would that eternity end up becoming normal for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for everything I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:36.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:46.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's my seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:49.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it says you're right behind the class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just come out of nowhere and sit by Kitakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:03.35,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She would never be able to interact with \NHarima Mika the same way ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:08.57,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not that's a good thing is something only she herself knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.34,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:14.36,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe people don't really understand themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.02,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,All they can do is keep evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:20.28,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That man's words echoed throughout the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:25.89,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,After doing something so bold, he thought he could do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:29.78,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He never thought for a split second...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:34.55,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That it would take so much courage to ask out a girl from his class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:43.05,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Time remaining until he reaches the girl: thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:48.18,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Time remaining until he finds his friend hitting on the girl: thirty-five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:52.44,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Time remaining until he delivers a powerful kick to his friend: forty-five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:56.96,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Time remaining until she turns down his offer of tea: seventy-five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:02.45,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Time remaining until he invites her to eat lunch with him on the roof: seventy-eight seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:06.08,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Time remaining until he falls in love with her:...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:09.83,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Time remaining until he confesses to her:...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:17.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you did something idiotic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:24.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You threw it all away for the sake of your brother's twisted love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:37.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, your twisted love for your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:39.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, aren't you in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:41.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's that merger with Nebula, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:44.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If word of this were to get out because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:50.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mafia or a really skilled sniper might \Nshoot you right between the eyes like, "Bam!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A cleaning crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:56.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the way they always pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:56.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:04.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Things have gotten a little more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you leave that room right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:13.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have a double checkmate, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:18.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your uncle was just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:25.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He believed in that world less than anyone, feared death \Nmore than anyone, and revered Heaven more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:28.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That world does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:36.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that all dullahans are female.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:37.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:38.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:43.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my subordinates was researching that for a while, but since I deemed it pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A rationalist, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:47.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:51.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this heaven—although it's \Ntechnically not a heaven—called Valhalla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:59.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In Scandanavian legend there are female angels clad in armor \Ncalled valkyries who take the souls of brave soldiers to Valhalla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Women who greet the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:04.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that story sound familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:10.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a theory that dullahans are the\N forms of valkyries wandering the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:13.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For her awakening, for battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:19.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All to search for sacred soldiers to admit into Valhalla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:24.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's alive, it hasn't awakened because this isn't a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:28.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I'd like to be chosen as a soldier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:33.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do if Valhalla truly awaits one after death?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:37.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt I could go to a war zone and prove myself there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:40.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have to make a war break out that only I can cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:41.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:44.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:52.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in the afterlife, I live a life such that I'll\N never get into Heaven, yet I meet a fallen angel because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:55.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all just speculation on your part.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:57.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who believe get saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, didn't I say this is just an insurance policy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:06.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I exist, I don't care whether I \Ngo to Hell or if there's only suffering there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:11.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if I can, I'd rather go to Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:14.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ms. Namie, let's all go to Heaven together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:18.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of The Dollars, I'll hold on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:20.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to see what's right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:25.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Celty would ever guess that her head's part of the same group she belongs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:29.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you should join The Dollars, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:33.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss likes to drag our new recruits into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:38.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm the one who's been doing most of the recruiting lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:43.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this fallen angel flap her wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:44.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.19,0:24:16.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her everyday life:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:18.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happens in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.77,0:24:20.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:25.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet some things are born and some \Nthings disappear in this city every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.87,0:24:28.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: Sudden Twist.
